Body: !!! IMPORTANT ANNOUNCEMENT FROM SWISSREALCOIN !!!  Dear Bounty Community,  As you know, we had to move our ICO back for about 3 months, while we work on activating our Plan B. This results in us having to pause the bounty program for the moment. Starting tonight, the bounty program is on hold until further notice, while we work on our Plan B for the ICO. Compliance and integrity towards our investors and our community are our top priorities.  The good news is, that we are planning to launch a new bounty program soon and that it gives all of you more time to earn more $SRC tokens, as the bounty period overall will be longer.  What happens now? We have registered all of your bounty posts and you will receive all tokens you have earned so far after a successful ICO (if minimum cap is reached). We will keep sharing progress updates in this chat here and on BitcoinTalk, so you know what’s going on on our side. As soon as we have worked out the details for plan B, we are planning to continue a new and great bounty program with a strong support team and you all can participate in it again to earn more tokens.  If you have any questions, please reach out to us anytime in our Bounty Chat on Telegram. It is very important to us to handle this with care and to consider our community's inputs and feedback.  https://t.me/swissrealcoinbounty  Best, The SwissRealCoin team

Regulatory Framework for Security Tokens in Switzerland https://medium.com/swissrealcoin/unclear-regulatory-framework-for-security-tokens-in-switzerland-17f035ea8c8f  We are extending the reservation phase and moving the start of the ICO for SwissRealCoin 2–3 months back. In the meantime we’re activating Plan B after the Swiss regulator FINMA missed the opportunity to provide clear guidance on the proper structuring of innovative security tokens.  SwissRealCoin (SRC) has applied for a letter of no action from FINMA in February 2018. The aim was to launch the SRC ICO in May 2018 in compliance with the newly issued FINMA ICO guidelines. Despite Switzerland’s pole position as ‘Crypto Nation’, the regulatory framework for security token projects remains unclear. After missing clear guidance from FINMA on how to structure innovative tokens in a fully compliant way, we have decided with our lawyers to activate Plan B, which will allow to launch the project in full compliance with the local regulatory framework. Preparing this new set-up, however, will delay the ICO.

Author: gerymakgyaer
Title: 🏘️ SWISSREALCOIN BOUNTY 🌏 1.500.000 CHF 🌏 FIRST REAL ESTATE CRYPTO (STOPPED)
Body: Unclear Regulatory Framework for Security Tokens in Switzerland https://medium.com/swissrealcoin/unclear-regulatory-framework-for-security-tokens-in-switzerland-17f035ea8c8f  We are extending the reservation phase and moving the start of the ICO for SwissRealCoin 2–3 months back. In the meantime we’re activating Plan B after the Swiss regulator FINMA missed the opportunity to provide clear guidance on the proper structuring of innovative security tokens.  SwissRealCoin (SRC) has applied for a letter of no action from FINMA in February 2018. The aim was to launch the SRC ICO in May 2018 in compliance with the newly issued FINMA ICO guidelines. Despite Switzerland’s pole position as ‘Crypto Nation’, the regulatory framework for security token projects remains unclear. After missing clear guidance from FINMA on how to structure innovative tokens in a fully compliant way, we have decided with our lawyers to activate Plan B, which will allow to launch the project in full compliance with the local regulatory framework. Preparing this new set-up, however, will delay the ICO.
